 <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/atalla-ayan/" rel="tag">Atalla Ayan</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/don-giovanni/" rel="tag">Don Giovanni</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/hans-georg-wegner/" rel="tag">Hans-Georg Wegner</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/johannes-knecht/" rel="tag">Johannes Knecht</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/matthias-holle/" rel="tag">Matthias Hölle</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/moritz-lobeck/" rel="tag">Moritz Lobeck</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/opera-lirica/" rel="tag">Opera lirica</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/pumeza-matshikiza/" rel="tag">Pumeza Matshikiza</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/rebecca-von-lipinski/" rel="tag">Rebecca von Lipinski</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/ronan-collett/" rel="tag">Ronan Collett</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/shigeo-ishino/" rel="tag">Shigeo Ishino</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/simone-schneider/" rel="tag">Simone Schneider</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/staatsoper-stuttgart/" rel="tag">Staatsoper Stuttgart</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/wolfgang-amadeus-mozart/" rel="tag">Wolfgang Amadeus Mozart</a><meta itemprop="keywords" content="André Morsch, Andrea Moses, Antony Hermus, Atalla Ayan, Don Giovanni, Hans-Georg Wegner, Johannes Knecht, Matthias Hölle, Moritz Lobeck, Opera lirica, Pumeza Matshikiza, Rebecca von Lipinski, Ronan Collett, Shigeo Ishino, Simone Schneider, Staatsoper Stuttgart, Wolfgang Amadeus Mozart"> </span> </footer></div> </article><div id="author-block" class="box-shadow-2px clearfix" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"><h2 class="author-title">About the author</h2><div id="author-avatar"> <img itemprop="image" style="display:none;" src="http://gravatar.com/avatar/e15610f34674f02caf174515ea5136d4" alt="" /> <img src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2008/04/Mussomeli1-132x200.jpg" width="66" height="100" alt="Gianguido Mussomeli" class="avatar avatar-100 wp-